<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n42004d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42004d">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42004d"> 4(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Pusery</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">With what supreme distress, disgust, and surprise we see, to-day, a great part of the noble Episcopal Church of England struck by a plague which seems incurable, under the name of Puseyism or Ritualism and bringing again&mdash;more or less openly&mdash;in many places the diabolical and filthy auricular confession among the Protestants of England, Australia, and America. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 7</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
